Summary: Change pending task mark to "P"
Keywords: 

	* planner.el (planner-publishing-markup): Accept P as task status.
	(planner-marks-regexp): Accept P as task status.
	(planner-renumber-tasks): Sort pending, then delegated, then
	completed, then cancelled tasks.
	(planner-markup-task): Mark up pending tasks.
	(planner-task-pending): Change pending task mark to P.
        Thanks to Ephrem for the feature request.
        
        * planner.el (planner-list-unfinished-tasks): Consider
        cancelled tasks finished.
